  <!--
    Deliberately incomplete, three keys of eight, and the window caption is not one of them.

    This is what a translation in progress looks like, which is what most translations are for most of their life.
    Every key missing here falls back to the neutral language on its own, so the window mixes German and English
    rather than losing the German it does have, or showing an empty string where a translation has not arrived.

    German also makes the other localization problem visible, its text runs about a third longer than English,
    which is what breaks a layout that was only ever looked at in the language it was written in.
  -->
  <data name="Heading" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Ein Ort für jeden Text</value>
  </data>
  <data name="Intro" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Alles, was Sie in diesem Fenster lesen, stammt aus einer .resx-Datei, die in die Anwendung kompiliert wurde. Die Seite enthält keinen eigenen Text, und die Fensterbeschriftung ebenso wenig.</value>
  </data>
